{
  "stem": "12494.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And-- then as he usually did, around 2:00 PM, he came home for a late lunch, and he didn't know anything.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so we told him what happened.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the general was very explicit, he said that, Mr.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Stern, tomorrow morning, the Germans will come at 5 o'clock in the morning to arrest you.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You should not be here by the time they come.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You got to go away somewhere.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They explained that that's not going to be too bad, because after a while the Germans are going to issue safety passes to anybody who was recommended by the-- by the Jewish Council, the so-called-- the Judenrat.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But that he had to disappear for a few days because, otherwise, he would be arrested.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So we packed up, and went to-- to-- called on the phone, and went to a brother of my father's.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, we all went-- left the place.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the general was wrong, he didn't come on Monday morning, he came on Wednesday morning.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But we weren't home.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We stayed away for a week, and then after-- all kinds of things happened during that week, I just say it from the point of view of our family-- our little family.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Then [SIGHS] within eight or nine days, Dad got his protective pass, and then we could go back home.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But that was essentially our-- our reaction to the occupation.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Plus a number of other things like, the general told my dad, [INAUDIBLE] look, Mr.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Stern.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Arthur is 19 years old, he's an adult.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You've got to understand that he will have to stand on his own from now on.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You've got to give him a lot of money so he can buy himself out of any situation.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
